headline: Stipulated agreement reached to help keep electricity affordable and meet future energy demand in Georgia
summary: Good news for Georgia families and businesses: Georgia Power has reached an agreement with the Public Interest Advocacy (PIA) Staff of the Georgia Public Service Commission (PSC) that, if approved, will help lower energy costs—all while meeting growing electricity demand across the state.
